四散周圍去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:59:28.000Z","msg":"咁油尖旺都無咩地方可以四散，太散又變落單"},{"pid":"b3c93efa434e3d677711fbb87629f2f02f247501","tid":1398664,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:05:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到時又會有人死守，後面d人叫前面唔肯走又跟住唔走話</span></span>"},{"pid":"1dba91b78bb31759cfc482d7b46e03409aa51672","tid":1398664,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"要做到好似呢2日馬鞍山咁"},{"pid":"9afc6d682b4f82ecefabc3cec7a57e117b149f88","tid":1398664,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c41b959ace7dd12915fbbfef7b5dedcd81d36a34","tid":1398664,"uid":43833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:48:42.000Z","msg":"記住be water, 唔好死守前線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1398880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1398880</a>"},{"pid":"5c2cb0ed1dbf3ff5be555af560ebdfd0e42f9620","tid":1398664,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:49:27.000Z","msg":"膠鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909632fbb09ad5dc525d028acbb2f43868475d93","tid":1398664,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:52:45.000Z","msg":"大家記得轉場呀"},{"pid":"293d09a7348725bd6779fb12a24cc5ec370013e3","tid":1398664,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e4563af917fbc1a472e1196d279e87327cfe93","tid":1398664,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06: